Chicken-UI Pseudo Code


Add some Chicken Details 
 
CREATE chickens list 
PRINT main menu options 
GET user input for main menu option 
 
IF user input is 0: 
   	EXIT app 
 
# Main Menu 
ELSE IF user input is 1: 
 
   	PRINT main menu options 
   	GET user input for main menu option 
 
    	IF user input is 0: 
        		RETURN to main menu 
 
   	ELSE IF user input is 1: 
        		PRINT chickens list 
 
    	ELSE IF user input is 2: 
 
# CREATE new chicken 
        		GET user input for chicken name 
        		APPEND product name to products list 
 
    	ELSE IF user input is 3: 
     
        	# STRETCH GOAL - UPDATE existing chicken 
        		PRINT chicken names with its index value 
        		GET user input for chicken index value 
        		GET user input for new chicken name 
        		UPDATE chicken name at index in chickens list 
 
    	ELSE IF user input is 4: 
 
        	# STRETCH GOAL - DELETE chicken 
        	PRINT chickens list 
        	GET user input for chicken index value 
       	 DELETE chicken at index in chickens list 
